Wendy Felecia Philander (née Kaizer) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na-eje ozi dị ka onye otu Western Cape Provincial Parliament kemgbe Ọgọst 2018
Ọ bụ onye isi oche nke Standing Committee on Health
Ọ bụbu onye otu Kọmitii Mayoral nke Drakenstein Local Municipality
Philander bụ onye otu Democratic Alliance

A mụrụ Philander na New York, obodo Paarl nke ndị na-arụ ọrụ.
Ọ bụ nwa nwanyị nke Mary na Jack Kaizer
Nne ya nwụrụ mgbe ọ nọ na klas 11
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị Paulus Joubert na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Paulus Joubert. Ọ ghọrọ onye otu Democratic Alliance na 2008
A họpụtara Philander dị ka onye kansụl mpaghara DA nke Drakenstein Local Municipality na ntuli aka obodo nke afọ 2011

Mgbe ntuli aka ime obodo nke afọ 2016 gasịrị, ọ ghọrọ onye kansụl PR maka DA na ime obodo. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ ugboro abụọ dị ka onye otu Mayoral Committee for Human Settlements and Health n'oge Gesie van Deventer na Conrad Poole bụ ndị isi obodo.

N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2018, a ṅụrụ Philander iyi dị ka onye otu Western Cape Provincial Parliament, na-anọchi Lennit Max. E kenyere ya ọrụ na kọmitii Social Cluster. Mgbe ntuli aka nke Mee 2019 gasịrị, a ṅụrụ ya iyi maka oge mbụ ya zuru ezu na 22 Mee 2019
Ọ bụ naanị onye omeiwu si na obodo Drakenstein
Na June 2019, a họpụtara Philander ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi oche nke Kọmitii Na-ahụ Maka Ahụike.
Philander bụ onye isi otu Democratic Alliance Women's Network (DAWN)
Ọ bụ onye isi oche mpaghara nke netwọk ahụ
Ọ bụkwa onye otu kọmitii na-ahụ maka mpaghara nke Democratic Alliance.
N'ọnwa Nọvemba 2020, ọ gbara ọsọ maka onye isi mpaghara DA mana onye isi mpaghara Bonginkosi Madikizela meriri ya
Philander nwetara ọnụọgụ nke abụọ kachasị elu na 255 mgbe Madikizela (444) sochiri onye na-ekwuchitere ndị omeiwu mpaghara, Masizole Mnqasela (210).
N'abalị asaa n'ọnwa Mee afọ 2022, ọ guzoro maka osote onye isi mpaghara nke DA na nzukọ kansụl mpaghara nke pati ahụ iji họpụta onye isi mpaghara ọhụrụ
Ọ meriri JP Smith.
Àtụ:Members of the Western Cape Provincial Parliament
